{"id":["109274915688993375"],"username":["debivort"],"acct":["debivort@drosophila.social"],"display_name":["Ben de Bivort"],"locked":[false],"bot":[false],"discoverable":[false],"group":[false],"created_at":["2022-11-02"],"note":["<p>Professor at <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/Harvard\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Harvard<\/span><\/a> University in Organismic and Evolutionary Biology <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/OEB\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>OEB<\/span><\/a> and the Center for Brain Science <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/CBS\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>CBS<\/span><\/a>. <\/p><p>We study the <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/behavior\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>behavior<\/span><\/a> of individual flies as a model of <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/individuality\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>individuality<\/span><\/a> and <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/personality\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>personality<\/span><\/a>, and manifestation of <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/phenotypic\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>phenotypic<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/variability\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>variability<\/span><\/a>. We investigate the mechanistic basis of this variation through the lenses of <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/circuit\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>circuit<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/neuroscience\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>neuroscience<\/span><\/a>, <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/genetics\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>genetics<\/span><\/a> and <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/evolution\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>evolution<\/span><\/a>, with the tools of <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/computational\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>computational<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/ethology\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>ethology<\/span><\/a><\/p><p>lab.debivort.org<\/p><p>Other: <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/GJP\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>GJP<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/superforecaster\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>superforecaster<\/span><\/a>, <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/MIT\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>MIT<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://drosophila.social/tags/MysteryHunt\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>MysteryHunt<\/span><\/a><\/p>"],"url":["https://drosophila.social/@debivort"],"avatar":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/avatars/109/274/915/688/993/375/original/151ebf8ab6ee5951.png"],"avatar_static":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/avatars/109/274/915/688/993/375/original/151ebf8ab6ee5951.png"],"header":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/headers/109/274/915/688/993/375/original/20e9675054515117.jpg"],"header_static":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/headers/109/274/915/688/99